July 1, 2022, marks the 101st anniversary of the founding of the Communist Party of China (CPC), which has more than 96 million members. Many more wish to join in. Fung Fu-wing, a teacher from Hong Kong working in Guangzhou City, south China's Guangdong Province, is among those who have applied to become a Party member. He said he was inspired by what he has seen on the Chinese mainland.